ionally established military control over Syrian territory and conditioned withdrawal on their security requirements, which satisfies the market definition.\n\nThe preponderance standard is met by the official Israeli admissions of control combined with UN verification of the territorial violation."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019f15b0d6591bbedec29f86b616915e","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\": \"demonstrated\", \"rationale\": \"The preponderance of evidence demonstrates Israel commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over Syrian territory. Official Israeli statements confirm"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\": \\\"demonstrated\\\", \\\"rationale\\\": \\\"The preponderance of evidence demonstrates Israel commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over Syrian territory. Official Israeli statements confirm","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782775324537,"responseId":"gen-1782775324-8wUJWyDi736O2ssbst1Y"}}
