- PX-6 and PX-7: Credible reporting confirming IDF presence on the Syrian side of Mount Hermon (outside Golan Heights carveout)\n- PX-2 and PX-5: Additional official Israeli statements about taking over positions and continued deployment\n\nThe key question is whether this constituted a \"military offensive intended to establish control.\" While the defense argues the \"temporary\" and \"defensive\" nature negates this, the proposition's language does not require permanent control or aggressive motive. The evidence shows Israel intentionally established military control over Syrian territory and conditioned withdrawal on their security requirements, which satisfies the market definition.\n\nThe preponderance standard is met by the official Israeli admissions of control combined with UN verification of the territorial violation."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019f15b0d6591bbedec29f86b616915e","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\": \"demonstrated\", \"rationale\": \"The preponderance of evidence demonstrates Israel commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over Syrian territory. Official Israeli statements confirm taking control of the buffer zone in Syria, UNDOF verified IDF presence in the area of separation as a treaty violation, and credible reporting establishes this occurred on the Syrian side of Mount Hermon outside the Golan Heights carveout between September-December 2024."},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\": \\\"demonstrated\\\", \\\"rationale\\\": \\\"The preponderance of evidence demonstrates Israel commenced a military offensive intended to establish control over Syrian territory. Official Israeli statements confirm taking control of the buffer zone in Syria, UNDOF verified IDF presence in the area of separation as a treaty violation, and credible reporting establishes this occurred on the Syrian side of Mount Hermon outside the Golan Heights carveout between September-December 2024.\\","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"deepseek/deepseek-v3.1-terminus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782775324537,"responseId":"gen-1782775324-8wUJWyDi736O2ssbst1Y"}}
